      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STAR CASINO (1) made it two on the bounce in the most comprehensive of fashion here last time when putting the best part of 8L to his nearest rival. Has struck a purple patch and can keep the ball rolling. NEVER SURRENDER (4) was a gutsy winner two back before running headfirst into STAR CASINO last start. Meets the winner 3.5kgs better this time which can bridge some of the gap. HUBRISTIC (7) drove hard to arrive in the shadows of the post here last time. Brings different form that can threaten. CHEF MILITAIRE (2) has run into two dominant winners in his last two but has still battled away soundly into the placings. Gets an important 2kg claim and remains in the mix. WAKOOL ASH (6) was a dominant maiden winner here two back and then followed it up with a solid effort last time. Drawn cosy and deserves respect.",
